description: This header file defines APIs related to a Log Agent component within a broader data model. It declares functions for getting and setting parameters of various types (ulong, string, bool), and for committing changes. It also includes licensing information and module description, indicating its role in supporting a data model library for COSA components.

methods.name: LogAgent_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves a ULONG value for a specified parameter name for the log agent.

methods.name: LogAgent_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets a ULONG value for a specified parameter name for the log agent.

methods.name: LogAgent_Commit
methods.description: Commits any changes made to log agent parameters.

methods.name: LogAgent_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string value for a specified parameter name for the log agent.

methods.name: LogAgent_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string value for a specified parameter name.

methods.name: LogAgent_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean value for a specified parameter name.

methods.name: LogAgent_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean value for a specified parameter name.
